IV) D) combine the following 2 sentences into one sentence :
  1) ryouri wa oishi kunai desu + imouto ga tsukuri mashita = imouto ga tsuku-ta ryouri wa oishi kunai desu
  2) hito to ke-kon shita kunai desu + ryouri ga deki masen = ryouri ga deki nai hito to ke-kon shita kunai desu
  3) gaikujin o kiga shite imasu + nihon no shuukan ni tsuite yoku shi-te imasu = nihon no shuukan ni tsuite yoku shi-tei rugai kokujin o saga shite imasu
  4) hito ni mou ichigo ai tai desu + kiyounen no natsu ni ai mashita = kyonen no natsu nia-ta hito nimou ichi do aitai desu
  5) hito to ru-mumeeto ni narita kunai desu + yoku shaberi masu = yoku shaberu hito torou mumeeto ni nari taku nai desu
  6) kaisha wa kono tate mou no naka ni arimasu + ojisan ga hatarai dei masu = oji san ga hatara ite iruka isha wa kono tate mono no nakani arimasu
  7) fuyu yasumi ni ryokan ni tomarou toomo imasu + onsen ga arimasu = fuyu yasumi ni onsen ga aru ryokan ni tomarou toomo-teimasu
  8) ryuukan ni kiyoumi ga ariun desu ka? + gakusei o shi-te imasu ka? amerika ni ryuugaku shita koto ga arimasu = 
    ryuu gaku nikyou miga arun desu ga、amerika ni ryuu gaku shita koto ga aru gakusei o chi-tei masuka
